cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image feature matching between different imaging modalities, specifically RGB and thermal imaging. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The approach used involves deep learning and feature transfer, which are also relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper evaluates the approach using image processing techniques, which could also fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) category.
